sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant System as System
    participant Database as Database

    User->>System: Initiate search query
    System->>Database: Perform full-text search
    Database-->>System: Return search results
    System->>User: Display search results

    User->>System: Apply filters (media, contacts)
    System->>Database: Fetch filtered results
    Database-->>System: Return filtered results
    System->>User: Display filtered results

    User->>System: Request chat history
    System->>Database: Retrieve chat history
    Database-->>System: Return chat history
    System->>User: Display chat history